				I encountered the Glacier bear after my second visit to the caves.  I took the advice of earlier posts and used the spell &quot;Sense Animal&quot;.  It saved me loads of time looking around and let me stop in for a quick visits.  Use it!<BR>
<BR>
The bear conned blue to me as a Lvl 30 Shaman.  It resisted all cold DD spells so I stacked a couple of DoTs and rooted it.  While rooted, I switched to my 2 handed blunt Ogre War Maul since I didnt need the extra wisdom items for the remaining battle.  Big Mistake!  I found out the hard way the the Glacier Bear is invunerable to non-magic weapons.  This required a quick switch back to the trusty Enamelled Black Mace to finish it off. Note: requires magic weapons.<BR>
